description:
muCommander is an open source, dual-pane file manager available on all major operating systems


What's Changed
- bump Gradle to v8.10.2 by @ahadas in #1279
- Update dictionary_ko.properties by @VenusGirl in #1280
- Do not display hidden files by default by @ahadas in #1283
- Bumped JediTerm and its deps to fix Terminal problem on jre 23+ #1281 by @pskowronek in #1285
- change the scope for gdrive from 'drive' to 'drive.file' by @ahadas in #1290
- Consider nested volumes in testVolumes by @ahadas in #1291
- Update SignPackage to sign pty4j-unix-spawn-helper by @ahadas in #1292
